title: Pure Flamenco (Nuevo Flamenco Passion)
description:
Pure Flamenco: Nuevo Flamenco Passion 
Release Date: 5/25/1999
Label: Neurodisc
Pure Flamenco' features today's top Flamenco guitarists, plus 8 exclusive tracks including a live performance by Ottmar Liebert! Flamenco music's roots are ancient in tradition. Originally, the music of a wandering people, the gypsies of Andalucia, Flamenco music has evolved into an ever-changing artform limited only by the interpretations of the artists who carry on the legacy and continue to mold and shape it's sound.
